## Goals

- At least one unit test per analyzer module (12 test files)
- CI pipeline that blocks merges to `main` when tests or lint fail
- `CHANGELOG.md` starting from v0.12.0 baseline
- `CONTRIBUTING.md` with build, test, lint, and PR instructions
- Verify all `docs/` feature specs are accurate with valid links
- Tag and publish v0.13.0 using the existing `release.yml`
- Authentication stays consistent — same env var convention as the current CLI
- No changes to existing analyzer logic or CLI commands

---

## Non-Goals

- No new analyzer modules
- No changes to existing analyzer logic or severity rules
- No web dashboard, MCP integration, or CLI changes
- Using external MCP tools (Context7, Atlassian, Notion, Microsoft Learn) to assist development — these are workflow aids for the developer, not product deliverables and not tracked in this spec

